     H            Y.
     FAFAPPNO UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FAGAPL31 UF  E           K        DISK
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@HIN1  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN2  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@LOTN  3
      *
     C                     MOVE P@HIN1    K@HIN1  5
     C                     MOVE P@HIN2    K@HIN2  5
     C                     MOVE P@HIN3    K@HIN3  2
      *
     C           HINKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN1  5
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN2  5
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN3  2
      * AGAPL31排他ロック確認
     C           HINKEY    CHAINAGAPL31              77
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@LOTN
      *
     C           HINKEY    CHAINAFAPPNO              88
      *
     C           *IN88     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '001'     WFLOTN
     C                     WRITEAFAPPNO1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE WFLOTN    N@LOTN  30
     C                     ADD  1         N@LOTN
     C                     MOVE N@LOTN    WFLOTN
     C                     UPDATAFAPPNO1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C           #DAMMY    BEGSR
     C                     UPDATAGAPL311
     C                     ENDSR
      *
